<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4974568>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. Corydoras brittoi, holotype, MNRJ 43316, 38.1 mm SL, Brazil, Mato Grosso State, Colniza Municipality, Guariba District, tributary to the rio Guariba, rio Aripuanã drainage, rio Madeira basin, 09°06’47.4”S 60°25’14.1”W. Dorsal (top), lateral (middle) and ventral (bottom) views. Photo by Celso Ikedo." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4974568/files/figure.png" .

