<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4974572>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Dorsal- and pectoral-fin spines of (a, c) Corydoras brittoi, NUP 17313, 34.1 mm SL, showing serrations directed towards the origins of the spines on posterior margins of the (a) dorsal-fin spine (8.6 mm long) and of the (c) right pectoral-fin spine (8.9 mm long), and of (b, d) Corydoras pavanelliae, NUP 17315, 26.8 mm SL, showing serrations directed towards the tips of the spines on posterior margins of the (b) dorsal-fin spine (7.9 mm long) and of the (d) right spine (7.6 mm long)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4974572/files/figure.png" .

